skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: big lake
des:
Live near Big Lake, Washington? This skill will help you stay on top of things. Want local weather conditions? Forget if it's recycle week? How about a local water conditions report? Or even what's on the menu for school lunch? This skill has you covered!

Phrases to try include:

Alexa, ask Big Lake How is the water? (or Should I go water skiing? or What are the water conditions?)
Alexa, tell Big Lake the lake is calm, (or choppy, or glassy, or stormy, or rough)
Alexa, ask Big Lake What's for school lunch today? (or tomorrow, or Friday, or on April 10th...)
Alexa, ask Big Lake Is it garbage day? (or When is garbage day, or Is it recycle week?)
Alexa, ask Big Lake for the weather
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
